This is the BESSY-scripts bundle.

it has the following directory-structure:

CVS: this script is needed for the CVS version control system

bin: all binaries (executables)

doc: all further documentation is found here

lib: libaries (e.g. perl-modules) are found here

src: module and script sources can be found here. This directory
     is not needed if you are no developer of scripts in this module.
